1
00:01:31,130 --> 00:01:35,740
(Destiny and Saving)

2
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:38,780
(Episode 26)

3
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:51,280
Po Yun.

4
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:55,280
Po Yun.

5
00:01:57,039 --> 00:01:57,800
My Lady.

6
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:01,290
You've suffered because of me.

7
00:02:01,760 --> 00:02:03,760
My Lady, please don't think that way.

8
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,780
That Chongguang

9
00:02:04,810 --> 00:02:06,210
didn't do anything to me.

10
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,380
My Lady, but why did you come back?

11
00:02:10,080 --> 00:02:12,170
There are still matters I haven't investigated clearly.

12
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:13,770
Of course, I had to come back.

13
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:16,560
My Lady, if you have anything left undone,

14
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:18,079
let me handle it for you.

15
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:21,160
Since you already left this place with Hero Mo Xiao,

16
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:23,490
you absolutely shouldn't have come back.

17
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:25,000
I must

18
00:02:25,560 --> 00:02:27,690
investigate that matter personally.

19
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:28,680
My Lady,

20
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,680
what is this matter?

21
00:02:31,530 --> 00:02:33,130
Tell me the truth, Po Yun.

22
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:36,410
Did my father practice any mysterious demonic techniques?

23
00:02:36,410 --> 00:02:38,040
Master Feng's Tianxing Secret Treasury

24
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:40,280
contained martial arts manuals from all around the world.

25
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,840
The techniques he practiced were wide-ranging and complex.

26
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:46,640
I don't know which specific technique you're referring to, My Lady.

27
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:49,720
Chongguang taught my father some mysterious demonic technique.

28
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,570
Do you know

29
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,800
if my father passed it on to anyone else?

30
00:02:57,410 --> 00:03:00,070
Although I followed Master Feng for many years,

31
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,650
I can't say for sure

32
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,610
whether he ever taught it to others

33
00:03:03,800 --> 00:03:05,130
in the sect.

34
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,960
My Lady, have you discovered something?

35
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:10,600
Back when Shushan disbanded the Tianxing Sect,

36
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,440
was it because they feared

37
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:14,160
that the demonic technique might spread within the sect?

38
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:16,020
Greetings, Star Lord of Shaohao.

39
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,079
The Supreme Lord has ordered me

40
00:03:17,079 --> 00:03:19,280
to bring the ceremonial attire that he personally oversaw to you.

41
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,410
Star Lord of Shaohao, please try it on.

42
00:03:22,390 --> 00:03:22,880
Let's go.

43
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:25,680
Star Lord of Shaohao, please try on the outfit now.

44
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,600
Just look at what you've done to Po Yun.

45
00:03:27,600 --> 00:03:28,530
He needs to rest.

46
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,079
Isn't it because of you

47
00:03:30,079 --> 00:03:31,410
that he's in this state?

48
00:03:32,280 --> 00:03:33,600
The Supreme Lord, considering his loyalty,

49
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:35,200
has already spared his life.

50
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,880
To prevent him from secretly escaping down the mountain with you,

51
00:03:37,880 --> 00:03:40,480
he had to be restrained here at Shaohao Palace.

52
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,520
Star Lord, instead of reflecting on your actions,

53
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:44,400
are you trying to blame the Supreme Lord now?

54
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,060
My Lady has no such intention.

55
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,560
Stop trying to stir up trouble here.

56
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:51,320
My Lady.

57
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,930
I'm not seriously injured.

58
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,260
I can go rest by myself for a while.

59
00:04:06,560 --> 00:04:08,560
Since you already left with Mo Xiao,

60
00:04:08,960 --> 00:04:10,220
why have you come back?

61
00:04:10,440 --> 00:04:12,240
What does that have to do with you?

62
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:14,560
You really think you're the Supreme Lord's consort now?

63
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,620
Do you know why he wanted to marry you?

64
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:19,370
What's it got to do with you?

65
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:22,560
Don't fool yourself into thinking he actually loves you.

66
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:24,160
He went to great lengths to marry you

67
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,180
only because you have

68
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:27,580
a Snow Realm Ice Blue Moth within your body.

69
00:04:28,840 --> 00:04:29,480
What?

70
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,240
Oh, so you didn't know?

71
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:34,970
Your father, Feng Xingtian,

72
00:04:34,970 --> 00:04:36,400
in order to save you back then,

73
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,280
offered a Snow Realm Ice Blue Moth

74
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,860
and gained the Supreme Lord's trust.

75
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:42,800
But he cunningly concealed

76
00:04:42,800 --> 00:04:45,400
the fact that Ice Blue Moths come in mother-child pairs.

77
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:47,720
He only presented the mother Ice Blue Moth to the Supreme Lord,

78
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:50,450
while the child Ice Blue Moth is inside your body.

79
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,610
Father,

80
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,960
play with me.

81
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:08,800
Lixue,

82
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,530
I was just about to look for you.

83
00:05:10,530 --> 00:05:11,160
Dad,

84
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,560
what are these?

85
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,310
They are

86
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:16,740
the most delicious candies in the world.

87
00:05:17,040 --> 00:05:19,040
I was just about to let you have some.

88
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:21,040
The most delicious candies?

89
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:25,920
Then... give it to me.

90
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,420
But you must remember,

91
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,600
this kind of candy must be swallowed whole.

92
00:05:30,720 --> 00:05:32,240
Otherwise, it won't be sweet.

93
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,100
Can you do that?

94
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,480
Lixue,

95
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:58,400
be a good girl.

96
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,820
Swallow it whole.

97
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,130
This way,

98
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:03,360
even if I'm not around someday,

99
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,920
it will still protect your life.

100
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,400
Perhaps its spiritual energy

101
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:08,600
can also help you get rid of the strange cold energy within your body.

102
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:09,400
In the future,

103
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:12,680
you won't need to carry that Ice Silkworm Cocoon anymore.

104
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:28,920
The Supreme Lord saved you 10 years ago

105
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:31,600
just to merge the mother and child Ice Blue Moths.

106
00:06:31,600 --> 00:06:33,000
And that's precisely why

107
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,280
he wants to marry you.

108
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,000
At that time,

109
00:06:36,159 --> 00:06:38,230
the Supreme Lord will gain supreme divine power

110
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:40,360
and greatly enhance his cultivation.

111
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:15,330
Star Lord Xuyuan, why aren't you staying properly in your Yaoling Palace

112
00:07:15,330 --> 00:07:16,930
and instead wandering here?

113
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:19,240
I came to visit you, Star Lord Ji.

114
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:20,560
"Visit?"

115
00:07:21,770 --> 00:07:22,580
What?

116
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:27,710
Star Lord Xuyuan, you and I broke into the Ancestral Hall's secret chamber together,

117
00:07:27,710 --> 00:07:30,770
yet Chongguang only imprisoned me in the Demon Prison.

118
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:33,940
Star Lord Xuyuan, have you come to comfort me

119
00:07:34,490 --> 00:07:36,290
to ease your guilty conscience?

120
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:39,280
Star Lord Ji, there's no need to harbor resentment.

121
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:41,159
Chongguang didn't punish me severely,

122
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:43,960
purely out of respect for the former Supreme Lord.

123
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:46,360
Everything you have done

124
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:49,300
is for the future of our Heavenly Demon Clan.

125
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,320
Back then,

126
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,050
you followed Yeyuan

127
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,810
and made great contributions to our clan.

128
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,850
Even if only for Yeyuan's sake,

129
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,480
I've always held

130
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:01,080
deep gratitude for you.

131
00:08:07,720 --> 00:08:09,120
In my heart...

132
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,800
I have always regarded you as the Supreme Consort.

133
00:08:15,400 --> 00:08:17,300
I only hope that you can...

134
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:22,410
regain the confidence you once had when assisting the former Supreme Lord

135
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:24,820
and rejuvenate the Heavenly Demon Sect.

136
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,160
We must not allow Chongguang

137
00:08:28,160 --> 00:08:29,960
to keep ruling the sect forever!

138
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,760
The former Supreme Lord left a final command

139
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:36,289
for Chongguang to temporarily hold the position of Demon Lord.

140
00:08:36,700 --> 00:08:39,299
As long as I find the child of Yeyuan and myself,

141
00:08:39,640 --> 00:08:40,730
Chongguang

142
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:44,540
will surely have to return the Heavenly Demon Sect to us.

143
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:46,670
Do you have any news, Star Lord Xuyuan?

144
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,000
Star Lord Ji.

145
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:52,080
Just put your mind at ease

146
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,610
and endure a little longer.

147
00:08:54,010 --> 00:08:55,470
When the time is right,

148
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:59,080
I will personally come to get you out.

149
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:13,000
Mo Xiao's injuries this time are indeed quite serious.

150
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,760
The Divine Healer is treating him now,

151
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:17,090
but it's still difficult to determine...

152
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,600
what the results will be after seven days.

153
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:19,160
What?

154
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,240
It's that serious?

155
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,420
Senior...

156
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:25,100
Where is Junior Xuan Zhen?

157
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,240
Where's she?

158
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,400
Junior Xuan Zhen's here.

159
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,640
Junior Xuan Zhen.

160
00:09:32,600 --> 00:09:33,360
Senior.

161
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:34,600
It's time.

162
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:38,120
I need to give you acupuncture now.

163
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:38,480
Come on.

164
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,120
Junior,

165
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,470
listen to me.

166
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:42,760
Please go to Peach Blossom Village.

167
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,440
Mo Xiao is seriously injured.

168
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,720
I won't be at ease if you don't go.

169
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,840
Senior,

170
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,240
the poison in your body hasn't been

171
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:51,360
completely eliminated yet,

172
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,060
which is why you're so weak.

173
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,200
You must understand

174
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,480
that I have to prioritize you, the Sect Leader.

175
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,840
As for the Young Sect Leader, he has the Divine Healer taking care of him.

176
00:09:58,840 --> 00:10:01,600
He doesn't need an old alchemist like me at the moment.

177
00:10:01,600 --> 00:10:02,540
It's nothing serious with me...

178
00:10:02,540 --> 00:10:03,840
Junior Xuan Zhen is right.

179
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:06,120
With Junior focusing on acupuncture treatment for you,

180
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:08,200
the remaining poison in your body will surely be completely removed.

181
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,080
As for Mo Xiao, let's wait for seven days

182
00:10:10,080 --> 00:10:11,720
and see what the Divine Healer says.

183
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:13,720
Right now, the most important thing

184
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,800
is to heal you first,

185
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,240
the Sect Leader.

186
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:18,600
Yes, Master.

187
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,760
Regarding the Young Sect Leader,

188
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:21,360
I will visit him personally.

189
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:22,720
Master, please rest assured and focus on your recovery.

190
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,640
Your health is of utmost importance.

191
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:26,920
The poison from this Rootless Flower is extremely potent.

192
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,840
Even after taking the antidote,

193
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:32,300
it's difficult to completely eliminate the residual toxins.

194
00:10:34,180 --> 00:10:36,580
If something were to happen to me one day...

195
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,230
Junior Murong.

196
00:10:38,880 --> 00:10:41,860
Remember to bring Mo Xiao back to the Shushan Sect

197
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,200
and help him take command.

198
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,280
Only then could I be at ease.

199
00:10:46,360 --> 00:10:48,990
Senior, why such pessimistic words?

200
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,360
With Junior taking care of you day and night,

201
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,140
you'll surely recover soon.

202
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,120
Besides,

203
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,520
the Young Sect Leader's trial still has three more years to go.

204
00:10:57,520 --> 00:10:59,120
The overall situation of our Shushan Sect

205
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,980
still requires your leadership.

206
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:06,120
Has the Young Sect Leader woken up?

207
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:06,600
No.

208
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,130
Zisu,

209
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,780
are you sure he doesn't have any other injuries

210
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:11,240
that you might've missed?

211
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:13,530
That shouldn't be the case.

212
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,520
I'll go check.

213
00:11:25,120 --> 00:11:26,180
Young Sect Leader.

214
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,460
How did he just disappear?

215
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:36,520
I don't know.

216
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:38,840
The Young Sect Leader hadn't made a sound this whole time in the room.

217
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,760
Right, Zimu?

218
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:43,800
He wouldn't have gone to Mount Suyu again, would he?

219
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,380
He shouldn't have.

220
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,360
I don't think he would be that impulsive anymore.

221
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,960
Ever since Feng Lixue appeared,

222
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:51,020
when has he ever not acted on impulse?

223
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:54,750
I know where he is.

224
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:55,610
Come with me.

225
00:12:15,420 --> 00:12:16,070
Lixue.

226
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:19,960
Try this.

227
00:12:24,960 --> 00:12:25,700
Well done.

228
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:28,380
Then I'll reward you with one of these.

229
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,450
What's this?

230
00:12:29,880 --> 00:12:30,760
Rabbit food.

231
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:31,580
I don't want it.

232
00:12:31,580 --> 00:12:32,280
Come on, eat it.

233
00:12:32,280 --> 00:12:33,070
I won't.

234
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:34,080
Just one bite!

235
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,550
Let go of me.

236
00:13:51,520 --> 00:13:53,580
You escorted me down the mountain...

237
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,240
just to say goodbye to me.

238
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:58,640
Lixue.

239
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:01,600
Were those three days...

240
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:05,060
really all the time we can share in this life?

241
00:14:10,500 --> 00:14:11,640
Mo Xiao!

242
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:31,320
You've been unconscious the whole time,

243
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,840
so I didn't have a chance to ask you.

244
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,480
She came down the mountain with you,

245
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:37,340
but why are you the only one lying unconscious here?

246
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:38,570
Where is she?

247
00:14:39,830 --> 00:14:40,590
She left.

248
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:41,720
Left?

249
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:43,050
Where did she go?

250
00:14:44,360 --> 00:14:45,430
Mount Suyu.

251
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,080
Why did she go back?

252
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:49,840
Lixue...

253
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:53,760
she's not a woman who willingly lives under someone else's protection.

254
00:14:53,760 --> 00:14:56,090
There are some things she must do herself.

255
00:14:58,520 --> 00:14:59,600
If that's the case,

256
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:02,260
why did she risk offending the Demon Lord

257
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,620
just to accompany you down the mountain?

258
00:15:04,950 --> 00:15:07,350
She did that to escort me down the mountain,

259
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,470
to protect me...

260
00:15:14,360 --> 00:15:16,880
and to fulfill my wish.

261
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,110
Don't you

262
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:22,480
have anything to say to me?

263
00:16:23,720 --> 00:16:24,480
Master.

264
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,000
I already know

265
00:16:28,120 --> 00:16:30,780
that the one who killed my father wasn't Mo Xiao.

266
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:35,240
It was you.

267
00:16:37,760 --> 00:16:41,820
My father died because he practiced your mysterious demonic technique.

268
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:45,780
So, you came back this time...

269
00:16:46,600 --> 00:16:48,130
to seek revenge on me?

270
00:16:58,600 --> 00:17:00,880
Master, I'm grateful for your gift of rebirth

271
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:02,160
and for raising me.

272
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:03,650
Now,

273
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:06,260
I have nurtured the Ice Blue Moth for you.

274
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,680
Please, Master, remove it from my body.

275
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:10,520
This way,

276
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,819
