00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,280
ends here.

527
00:31:55,440 --> 00:31:58,160
"Ends here," you say?

528
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:03,560
You can't bring yourself to hate me

529
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:06,960
or love me?

530
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:14,120
Fine.

531
00:32:20,040 --> 00:32:20,640
Fine!

532
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,880
I'll grant your wish!

533
00:32:26,730 --> 00:32:29,260
Everything I've bestowed upon you before...

534
00:32:30,080 --> 00:32:30,880
today...

535
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:34,240
I'll take it all back!

536
00:32:38,800 --> 00:32:40,050
From now on,

537
00:32:40,180 --> 00:32:42,280
all ties between us are severed!

538
00:33:14,520 --> 00:33:18,220
I hereby announce to all members of the Heavenly Demon Sect:

539
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:21,790
from this day forth, Feng Lixue, the Star Lord of Shaohao,

540
00:33:22,040 --> 00:33:23,720
is no longer a member of our sect,

541
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:25,280
nor is she my disciple!

542
00:33:26,200 --> 00:33:29,740
I have taken back all the demonic techniques I passed down to her.

543
00:33:29,740 --> 00:33:31,100
From this day forward,

544
00:33:31,650 --> 00:33:33,570
Feng Lixue shall have no connection

545
00:33:33,570 --> 00:33:34,850
to me, Chongguang,

546
00:33:34,870 --> 00:33:36,550
nor to Mount Suyu!

547
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:40,100
She is to be driven from Mount Suyu immediately!

548
00:34:25,489 --> 00:34:27,900
I've followed you for many years, Supreme Lord,

549
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:29,179
but this is the first time I've seen you

550
00:34:29,179 --> 00:34:30,909
so disheartened and dejected.

551
00:34:32,040 --> 00:34:32,840
Supreme Lord,

552
00:34:33,610 --> 00:34:35,940
you still have a great destiny to fulfill.

553
00:34:36,190 --> 00:34:38,010
You must not lose yourself now.

554
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,080
The Young Sect Leader has returned.

555
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:00,140
Young Sect Leader.

556
00:35:03,850 --> 00:35:04,570
Lixue.

557
00:35:05,960 --> 00:35:09,440
In this life, I can only give you three days of happiness together.

558
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:10,610
From now on...

559
00:35:11,960 --> 00:35:14,960
I can only be the Young Sect Leader of the Shushan Sect.

560
00:35:24,160 --> 00:35:24,890
Senior,

561
00:35:25,080 --> 00:35:25,560
here.

562
00:35:26,200 --> 00:35:27,330
Take your medicine.

563
00:35:28,120 --> 00:35:28,760
Easy.

564
00:35:40,720 --> 00:35:41,470
Sect Leader,

565
00:35:41,600 --> 00:35:43,600
the Young Sect Leader has returned.

566
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:50,820
Looks like the Young Sect Leader, Jing, and the others have returned.

567
00:35:52,560 --> 00:35:53,040
Master,

568
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,640
respected senior masters,

569
00:35:54,640 --> 00:35:55,570
I have returned.

570
00:35:56,320 --> 00:35:57,850
It's good that you're back.

571
00:35:58,000 --> 00:35:59,060
Have your injuries

572
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:00,720
healed well?

573
00:36:05,040 --> 00:36:07,000
Thank you for your concern, Master and senior masters.

574
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,160
I have fully recovered.

575
00:36:08,160 --> 00:36:10,040
Young people do recover quickly.

576
00:36:10,760 --> 00:36:11,890
Do you know

577
00:36:12,280 --> 00:36:14,380
when you were severely injured and had to go to Peach Blossom Village

578
00:36:14,380 --> 00:36:16,480
to seek treatment from the Divine Healer Shi Bujiu,

579
00:36:16,480 --> 00:36:17,480
your master, myself,

580
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,000
and the other senior masters

581
00:36:19,000 --> 00:36:20,480
were all worried sick?

582
00:36:21,000 --> 00:36:22,460
But now that we see you

583
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,160
have returned safe and sound,

584
00:36:24,160 --> 00:36:26,120
we can finally put our minds at ease.

585
00:36:26,120 --> 00:36:26,880
Indeed.

586
00:36:27,520 --> 00:36:28,680
Sect Leader has now

587
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:30,400
been cured of the poison.

588
00:36:30,600 --> 00:36:32,880
Mo Xiao has also recovered and returned.

589
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,400
Shouldn't we...

590
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:36,100
celebrate this occasion?

591
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,280
Celebrate what?

592
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:44,840
This time, Mo Xiao

593
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:46,480
has breached the demon city,

594
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:50,320
rescuing many disciples of the immortal sects from the demon's lair.

595
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:52,040
All the fellow immortal sects across the realm

596
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,440
have praised our Shushan Sect

597
00:36:53,440 --> 00:36:54,960
greatly for this.

598
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:56,480
In a few days...

599
00:36:56,760 --> 00:37:00,440
it will be our annual gathering of the immortal sects.

600
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:02,720
At that time, all the major sects

601
00:37:02,760 --> 00:37:04,400
will gather here.

602
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:07,340
I'd like to take this opportunity

603
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:09,680
to officially pass the position of Sect Leader

604
00:37:09,680 --> 00:37:11,760
to Mo Xiao.

605
00:37:15,200 --> 00:37:16,400
Master, you must not.

606
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:18,200
My trial period has not yet concluded.

607
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:19,920
I'm not ready to shoulder such a heavy burden.

608
00:37:19,920 --> 00:37:20,920
Yes, Senior.

609
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,440
We had an agreement before

610
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:25,970
that Mo Xiao would undergo a trial for 3 years.

611
00:37:26,290 --> 00:37:27,960
The term is not yet up.

612
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,080
Sect Leader,

613
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:31,560
why are you suddenly bringing up the matter of succession?

614
00:37:31,560 --> 00:37:32,560
Yes, Senior.

615
00:37:32,840 --> 00:37:35,960
Are you in a hurry to become one of those carefree immortals already?

616
00:37:35,960 --> 00:37:36,890
That's perfect.

617
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,600
Why don't I also pass the position of Branch Leader to Lingyun?

618
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:41,840
We can follow the example of the Sword Sovereign from back then

619
00:37:41,840 --> 00:37:42,680
and go into seclusion for cultivation,

620
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:45,280
being free and unfettered as soon as possible.

621
00:37:45,480 --> 00:37:47,280
You? Seclude yourself?

622
00:37:47,560 --> 00:37:48,840
You're just thinking about

623
00:37:48,840 --> 00:37:51,700
Sect Leader's few bottles of good wine, aren't you?

624
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,880
Drinking alone

625
00:37:53,900 --> 00:37:55,500
-is always boring.
-Stop it.

626
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,060
Now,

627
00:37:58,200 --> 00:38:00,530
Chongguang already has two demon stones.

628
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:04,360
Fortunately, Mo Xiao severely wounded the Demon Sect

629
00:38:05,200 --> 00:38:07,360
and saved our righteous immortal sects

630
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:09,480
from being corrupted by the stone.

631
00:38:10,160 --> 00:38:12,880
But Chongguang will certainly not stop at this.

632
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,000
Next,

633
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:16,440
he will spare no effort

634
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:18,440
to find the third demon stone.

635
00:38:19,040 --> 00:38:21,800
Once he obtains all three demon stones,

636
00:38:22,280 --> 00:38:26,230
he will surely regain the prestige of Yeyuan from the past

637
00:38:26,330 --> 00:38:30,860
and lead the forces of the Seven Caves, Nine Netherworlds, and other demon sects.

638
00:38:30,870 --> 00:38:34,310
At that time, I'm afraid not only our immortal sects

639
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:38,120
but the entire world will be in peril.

640
00:38:38,200 --> 00:38:39,520
So, Sect Leader,

641
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,860
that's why you're in such a hurry to

642
00:38:40,860 --> 00:38:42,730
pass the position of Sect Leader to Mo Xiao,

643
00:38:42,730 --> 00:38:45,150
hoping that Mo Xiao will lead the righteous immortal sects

644
00:38:45,150 --> 00:38:47,630
to stop Chongguang's sinister schemes.

645
00:38:47,960 --> 00:38:50,490
Now that I've just recovered from poisoning,

646
00:38:51,340 --> 00:38:53,380
I'm still weak and frail.

647
00:38:55,330 --> 00:38:59,130
Mo Xiao has received the true teachings of Sword Sovereign Fengyue

648
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:01,160
and has dealt a heavy blow to the Demon Sect,

649
00:39:01,160 --> 00:39:03,760
rescuing many disciples of the immortal sects.

650
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:05,610
He is what everyone hopes for.

651
00:39:06,310 --> 00:39:08,200
Now, only Mo Xiao

652
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:12,310
can lead the righteous immortal sects

653
00:39:12,410 --> 00:39:15,050
and thwart Chongguang's vicious ambitions.

654
00:39:15,430 --> 00:39:16,130
But, Master...

655
00:39:16,130 --> 00:39:17,090
Say no more.

656
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,000
It's decided.

657
00:39:20,700 --> 00:39:23,020
Everyone... you may go now.

658
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:26,950
See you later, Sect Leader.

659
00:39:27,640 --> 00:39:28,170
Alright.

660
00:39:29,660 --> 00:39:30,470
Master.

661
00:39:31,170 --> 00:39:32,570
It's time for your medicine.

662
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:34,100
Let me help you back to rest.

663
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:35,120
No rush.

664
00:39:36,250 --> 00:39:37,090
Mo Xiao.

665
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:38,460
Come with me.

666
00:39:38,760 --> 00:39:40,360
I have something to tell you.

667
00:39:40,450 --> 00:39:41,180
Yes, Master.

668
00:39:48,290 --> 00:39:49,350
Jing, come here.

669
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:50,440
Father,

670
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,090
I've brought you some Peach Blossom Wine.

671
00:39:52,090 --> 00:39:53,220
Peach Blossom Wine?

672
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:55,010
Son, you know me well.

673
00:39:55,220 --> 00:39:55,840
Alright.

674
00:39:56,140 --> 00:39:57,340
You two go back first.

675
00:39:57,530 --> 00:39:59,790
I have a few words to say to your Senior Lu.

676
00:40:00,490 --> 00:40:02,370
What important matters do you have to discuss with him?

677
00:40:02,370 --> 00:40:03,840
He's not even from our Fengyu Branch.

678
00:40:03,840 --> 00:40:04,480
Alright.

679
00:40:04,480 --> 00:40:05,280
I will be back soon.

680
00:40:05,280 --> 00:40:05,580
Come on,

681
00:40:05,580 --> 00:40:06,570
take your sister back.

682
00:40:06,570 --> 00:40:07,200
Jing,

683
00:40:07,220 --> 00:40:08,760
I happen to have something to ask you.

684
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:10,820
-Let's go back first.
-Okay, go back.

685
00:40:15,590 --> 00:40:16,360
Jianchuan.

686
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:17,480
Jianchuan?

687
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:19,820
Master Changfeng.

688
00:40:20,240 --> 00:40:21,100
These past few days,

689
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:23,410
you've been by your master's side, taking care of him.

690
00:40:23,410 --> 00:40:25,060
It must have been tiring for you.

691
00:40:25,060 --> 00:40:27,060
Fortunately, Mo Xiao has returned now.

692
00:40:27,060 --> 00:40:29,120
You can finally get some proper rest.

693
00:40:29,480 --> 00:40:31,140
Thank you, Master Changfeng.

694
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,810
To be honest,

695
00:40:33,170 --> 00:40:36,860
your master indeed has high hopes for Mo Xiao.

696
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:38,860
However...

697
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:41,000
in my eyes,

698
00:40:41,210 --> 00:40:43,480
when it comes to upholding principles and maintaining composure,

699
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,810
you're the top.

700
00:40:46,590 --> 00:40:47,840
Thank you, Master Changfeng.

701
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:48,910
You flatter me.

702
00:40:49,260 --> 00:40:50,060
Oh, by the way,

703
00:40:50,620 --> 00:40:52,310
your master also mentioned

704
00:40:52,640 --> 00:40:53,600
that you are now

705
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:56,140
reciting the Heart-Calming Mantra, right?

706
00:40:56,140 --> 00:40:57,380
Your master must hope

707
00:40:57,670 --> 00:40:58,840
that you can

708
00:40:58,840 --> 00:41:00,560
cultivate yourself well.

709
00:41:01,710 --> 00:41:03,690
The side hall of the Divine Mechanism Hall

710
00:41:03,690 --> 00:41:06,360
contains many precious books and secret manuals from my Fengyu Branch.

711
00:41:06,360 --> 00:41:07,700
If you have time,

712
00:41:07,720 --> 00:41:09,010
you can go and take a look.

713
00:41:09,010 --> 00:41:09,530
Okay.

714
00:41:10,130 --> 00:41:11,780
Thank you, Master Changfeng.

715
00:41:11,780 --> 00:41:12,780
It's my pleasure.

716
00:41:13,690 --> 00:41:14,840
You're still young.

717
00:41:16,890 --> 00:41:17,570
Ce,

718
00:41:17,700 --> 00:41:19,100
what do you want to ask me?

719
00:41:19,150 --> 00:41:22,010
You even take me to this place where no one is around.

720
00:41:23,150 --> 00:41:25,610
What happened at the Peach Blossom Village?

721
00:41:26,170 --> 00:41:27,620
What do you mean?

722
00:41:28,250 --> 00:41:30,430
You suddenly sent a message saying Mo Xiao was seriously injured

723
00:41:30,430 --> 00:41:31,880
and needed to go to Peach Blossom Village for medical treatment.

724
00:41:31,880 --> 00:41:34,290
Yet it took you so long to return to the Shushan Sect.

725
00:41:34,290 --> 00:41:35,620
What exactly happened?

726
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:38,370
You won't tell Father and the Sect Leader,

727
00:41:38,370 --> 00:41:40,500
but you should at least tell me, right?

728
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:42,310
Everything I said is true.

729
00:41:42,810 --> 00:41:44,070
If you don't believe me, go ask Lingyun.

730
00:41:44,070 --> 00:41:44,980
Ask him?

731
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:46,510
Wasn't it he who taught you

732
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,810
all those tricks in the first place?

733
00:41:47,810 --> 00:41:49,290
Ce, what are you talking about?

734
00:41:49,290 --> 00:41:51,130
I don't understand at all.

735
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,240
Not even married yet,

736
00:41:53,260 --> 00:41:55,050
and you're already taking sides with an outsider.

737
00:41:55,050 --> 00:41:57,480
Keeping secrets from your brother with others.

738
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,740
No, it's not like that.

739
00:41:59,990 --> 00:42:00,630
Alright,

740
00:42:00,760 --> 00:42:01,640
I'll tell you.

741
00:42:02,240 --> 00:42:03,280
But you must not tell

742
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,810
Father and the Sect Leader.

743
00:42:06,680 --> 00:42:07,680
Actually...

744
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:09,280
actually...

745
00:42:09,600 --> 00:42:10,680
Mo Xiao

746
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:13,100
went to Mount Suyu again to rescue Lixue.

747
00:42:13,730 --> 00:42:15,770
He didn't go to Peach Blossom Village for treatment.

748
00:42:15,770 --> 00:42:18,560
Lingyun and I invited Shi Bujiu

749
00:42:18,980 --> 00:42:20,860
to put on an act for Senior Lu.

750
00:42:21,200 --> 00:42:22,600
I thought as much.

751
00:42:22,810 --> 00:42:24,470
Ce, please don't tell anyone.

752
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:25,640
This time,

753
00:42:25,750 --> 00:42:27,380
Mo Xiao is truly pitiful.

754
00:42:27,520 --> 00:42:28,770
He couldn't take Lixue back.

755
00:42:28,770 --> 00:42:30,560
For three whole days, he was completely despondent, lost in despair.

756
00:42:30,560 --> 00:42:33,220
Only then did he finally pull himself together.

757
00:42:33,730 --> 00:42:35,600
I hope he can let go of it all for good

758
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:37,270
and cast aside distracting thoughts.

759
00:42:37,270 --> 00:42:38,600
He must be strong enough

760
00:42:38,920 --> 00:42:40,600
to carry the burden of leading the Shushan Sect.
